<p>Caused by missing capability check for disabling and hiding.This has been fixed by adding the missing check.</p>

<h4><a href="https://bugs.open-xchange.com/show_bug.cgi?id=51572" rel="nofollow">51572</a> Moving files with and without description not working in drive</h4>

