<h4><a href="https://bugs.open-xchange.com/show_bug.cgi?id=50040" rel="nofollow">50040</a> Content pane not refreshed</h4>

<p>After deleting a folder in a external storage account the view wasn´t updated.With this fix the view is updated after deleting a folder.</p>

